sources.title: Good Against Evil (1977) Horror Movie | Dack Rambo, Elyssa Davalos | Full Movie, Subtitles
sources.description:
She became Satan's play thing! 
The course of true love is messed up when Satan claims Jessica as his own personal property. A writer, Andy Stuart, teams up with an exorcist, Father Kemschler, to battle Satan, and a group of Devil worshipers led by Mr. Rimmin.

Original title: Good Against Evil (1977) 

Director: Paul Wendkos
Writer: Jimmy Sangster
Stars: Dack Rambo, Elyssa Davalos, Richard Lynch & Kim Cattrall
Genre: Classics, Cult, Horror, made for TV movie

00:00 Full Movie
01:38  A woman desperately wants to see her baby in the hospital.
11:47  A woman's car gets damaged and she becomes frustrated with the man responsible, but he offers to fix it and takes her car as collateral.
17:32  A man and a woman meet for dinner and get to know each other's backgrounds and aspirations.
23:23  A drifter named Andy falls in love with a woman named Jessica, but she pushes him away due to a belief that she brings bad luck to the men she gets close to.
35:39  A conversation between Agnes and Jessica about a man in their lives, followed by a scene with Father Wheatley and Jessica talking about her upcoming wedding.
47:58  A conversation between a father and a couple about supernatural occurrences and a potential marriage.
1:02:28  A doctor informs Linda that her daughter, Cindy, will be fine after experiencing convulsions and drawing strange images.
1:06:52  A desperate mother seeks help from a priest to save her possessed child.
1:13:33  A man and a woman discuss the supernatural events happening around them.
